name: For Sale For Lease
overview: When it comes to your property or your business, the one person who knows it inside out and upside down is you. That’s why we firmly believe that the best person to sell your property, be it commercial or residential, is you and not an estate agent. For Sale For Lease is Australia’s largest for sale by owner and private house sales website and because we know you’ve got more than enough on your plate when it comes to selling your home or business we believe in lightening the load by cutting out the Real Estate agents, business brokers, and of course, their unwelcome commissions.
